1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,264
DR. THOMPSON: How's our patient doing today, Sofia?

2
00:00:03,264 --> 00:00:08,352
NURSE VALENCIA: Stable, doctor. The patient's vitals are looking good.

3
00:00:08,352 --> 00:00:14,256
DR. THOMPSON: Excellent. Let's take a look at the scans and see how the injury is healing.

4
00:00:14,256 --> 00:00:15,720
JAXON REED: What...what happened?

5
00:00:15,720 --> 00:00:20,352
NURSE VALENCIA: You were in an accident, Jaxon. You're safe now.

6
00:00:20,352 --> 00:00:22,872
JAXON REED: An accident? I don't remember anything.

7
00:00:22,872 --> 00:00:30,360
DR. THOMPSON: Don't worry, Jaxon. You've been through a lot. We'll get you back on your feet in no time.

8
00:00:30,360 --> 00:00:34,872
JAXON REED: I had a dream...I was driving, and then...and then something happened.

9
00:00:34,872 --> 00:00:39,360
NURSE VALENCIA: Try to relax, Jaxon. You're safe here.

10
00:00:39,360 --> 00:00:43,944
DR. THOMPSON: We'll do some more tests in the morning, and we'll get to the bottom of this.

11
00:00:43,944 --> 00:00:45,792
JAXON REED: I just want to go home...please.
